{"item_id":"7a5088454f:0","text":"对输入颜色 pattern 进行阈值化，以创建黑白 mask。衰减会定义从黑到白的渐变过渡。输出始终位于 0 到 1 之间。"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:1","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:2","text":"Input Color"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:3","text":"要进行阈值化的颜色 pattern。"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:4","text":"Channel"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:5","text":"此节点将作用于的输入通道："}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:6","text":"0: Red"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:7","text":"1: Green"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:8","text":"2: Blue"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:9","text":"3: Luminance"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:10","text":"4: Average"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:11","text":"Threshold"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:12","text":"发生从黑到白过渡时所使用的值。"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:13","text":"Transition Width"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:14","text":"此控件允许创建锐利或渐进的过渡。过渡宽度以阈值为中心。"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:15","text":"Transition Profile"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:16","text":"从黑到白的插值可用三种不同曲线计算："}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:17","text":"0: Linear"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:18","text":"1: Smooth"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:19","text":"2: Gaussian"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:20","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:31","text":"resultRGB"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:22","text":"阈值化后的 pattern，以单色颜色输出。"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:23","text":"resultR"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:24","text":"R 通道结果"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:25","text":"resultG"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:26","text":"G 通道结果"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:27","text":"resultB"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:28","text":"B 通道结果"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:29","text":"resultA"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:30","text":"如果存在 alpha，并且"}
{"item_id":"7a5088454f:32","text":"已连接，则返回 RGB 之后的通道。如果 RGB 未连接，则返回第一个通道。"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "7a5088454f:21", "text": "resultRGB"}
